To compile and install you need:
 - QT 4.2
 - FreePascal 1.9.4
 - SDL
 - SDL_net
 - SDL_mixer
 - SDL_image
 - SDL_ttf
 - CMake 2.4.0
 
To compile just type 
# cmake . 
or
# cmake -DCMAKE_CXX_FLAGS="flags" -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX="install prefix" -DDATA_INSTALL_DIR="data dir"
then
# make install

That's all! Enjoy!